==''Bad 25''==
{{Main|Bad 25}}
It was announced on May 3, 2012 that the Estate of Michael Jackson and Epic Records would be releasing a 25th anniversary album of ''Bad''. The album was named ''[[Bad 25]]'' and was released on September 18, 2012.<ref name="Bad 25 Announcement">{{cite web|url=http://www.michaeljackson.com/us/news/25th-anniversary-michael-jacksons-landmark-album-bad-celebrated-september-18-release-new-bad-25|title=25th Anniversary of Michael Jackson's Landmark Album Bad Celebrated With September 18 Release Of New Bad 25 Packages|accessdate=2012-06-30|publisher=michaeljackson.com|work=Sony Music|language=English}}</ref>

